OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1779123960
OL,3,CRed Arrows to miss 2026 Blackpool Air
OL,4,CShow
OL,6,FThe world-famous Red Arrows will not
OL,7,Fappear at this year's Blackpool Air
OL,8,FShow, organisers have confirmed.
OL,10,FThe iconic RAF display team drew huge
OL,11,Fcrowds to Blackpool's seafront in
OL,12,FAugust 2025, and have made regular
OL,13,Fappearances at the annual event.
OL,15,FBut this summer they will be
OL,16,Frecovering from a month-long tour
OL,17,Facross North America.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1779123960
OL,3,CRed Arrows to miss 2026 Blackpool Air
OL,4,CShow
OL,6,FThe squadron is due to be travelling
OL,7,Fthe US throughout July, and while they
OL,8,Fwill be back in the UK in time for the
OL,9,Fshow mandatory maintenance checks will
OL,10,Fkeep the planes grounded.
OL,12,FThe tour is expected to generate more
OL,13,Fthan #2.5bn in direct foreign
OL,14,Finvestment for the UK.
OL,16,FThe absence of the Red Arrows is a
OL,17,Fsetback for tourism bosses in
OL,18,FBlackpool, who are now working to
OL,19,Fconfirm a suitable replacement for the
OL,20,Fpopular event.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1779123960
OL,3,CRed Arrows to miss 2026 Blackpool Air
OL,4,CShow
OL,6,FHowever, organisers have promised that
OL,7,Fthe show will still feature major
OL,8,Fattractions, including the RAF Typhoon
OL,9,Fand Battle of Britain Memorial Flight
OL,10,Fdisplay teams.
OL,12,FWill Myles, Head of Visit Blackpool
OL,13,Fsaid: "Unfortunately the RAF Red
OL,14,FArrows will not perform at the 2026
OL,15,FBlackpool Air Show due to other
OL,16,Fcommitments.
OL,18,F"We know how much residents and
OL,19,Fvisitors look forward to seeing the
OL,20,Fteam over our seafront.
OL,26,@uD@GOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1779123960
OL,3,CRed Arrows to miss 2026 Blackpool Air
OL,4,CShow
OL,6,F"We fully respect the important role
OL,7,Fthey play in representing the UK at
OL,8,Fhome and around the world, and we look
OL,9,Fforward to welcoming them back in
OL,10,Ffuture years."
OL,12,FThe Blackpool Air Show remains one of
OL,13,Fthe UK's most iconic free events.
OL,15,FWill Myles added: "In the coming
OL,16,Fweeks, we will reveal the full
OL,17,Fprogramme of high-impact displays,
OL,18,Fcrowd favourites, and exciting new
OL,19,Fadditions that will ensure the event
OL,20,Fcontinues to deliver the world-class
OL,21,Fexperience our visitors expect."
OL,26,@rD@NO]wD@SOU}D@`O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
