PN,39505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1779123960
OL,3,CRed Arrows to miss 2026 Blackpool Air
OL,4,CShow
OL,6,FThe Red Arrows, who have been a
OL,7,Fhighlight of the Blackpool Air Show
OL,8,Fsince the 1990s, are expected to
OL,9,Freturn in 2027.
OL,11,FAn RAF Spokesperson said: "I can
OL,12,Fconfirm that due to the Royal Air
OL,13,FForce Aerobatic Team returning from
OL,14,Ftheir USA Tour and then a subsequent
OL,15,Fmandatory crew stand-down and aircraft
OL,16,Fmaintenance activity, the 'Red Arrows'
OL,17,Fwill not display at the Blackpool Air
OL,18,FShow 2026."
OL,26,@sD@[OUzD@KO]
